Authentication Setup

set_datim()

Store DATIM credentials

set_email()

Store USAID email

set_pano()

Store PEPFAR Panorama credentials

set_s3keys()

Store S3 Credentials `set_s3keys` stores your s3 keys using the `keyring` package. This will only need to done once. After running `set_s3keys(access, secret)`, RStudio API which will then store the keys in your OS credential store using `keyring`.

Tidying

clean_agency()

Clean data from fundingagency column `clean_agency` converts all funding agency names to upper case removes the HHS prefix for those agencies and moves State and USAID subsidiaries under their parent agencies
